p.
  The Support Tickets system supports Markdown and Gravatar display pictures, and is also responsive so it looks and works elegantly on different devices like tablets or smartphones. Long gone are the days of developing a web application for mobile and desktop as distinctly separate platforms. Users are now also expecting web applications to "refresh automatically" as a standard feature, which is why employing AngularJS was so important.

p.
  I've gained valuable experience in Ruby on Rails development, front-end JavaScript development, agile methodologies and pure teamwork in a development context. But what's even more exciting, and rewarding, is that there's a real world, customer-facing end product which is both an asset to DataCentred and something for me to look back upon proudly even after I've finished my degree.